檳<br />\n統一戰線大成功<br />\n<br />\n用反間計離間計<br />\n<br />\n不戰而勝<br />\n<br />\n全世界傳媒，議員開哂口話今次係變相公投<br />\n世界各國傳媒喺香港 議員嚟觀察<br />\n<br />\n但香港人畢竟多政治白痴<br />\n喺受薪三毛 分化撚橫行嘅鋪天蓋地宣傳下<br />\n唔團結 好有原則 好冇策略<br />\n對住個狡猾同最叻玩政治，最叻分化嘅政權 <br />\n條路自己揀<br />\n仆街唔好喊<br />\n<br />\n唉 我只係覺得好可惜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果輸咗<br />\n萬劫不復<br />\n<br />\n一定投反建制<br />\n得建制同熱狗對決 就為大局投lesser evil 熱狗<br />\n<br />\n大家聽日早啲去投票<br />\n全家總動員<br />\nCall齊親友</span>"},{"pid":"0b66494c96a4544bd08ec20a0fd76b9ef482d65e","tid":1747692,"uid":48868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:29:43.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n手足不是condom"},{"pid":"1a4e6a8e84f5fcf6fe1749366d47fe7a4502a06a","tid":1747692,"uid":156547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:32:47.000Z","msg":"「因為多你一票真係好多，每一票都係好關鍵」"},{"pid":"e16aa0539ebe6805a5855db53077c1f86e89c496","tid":1747692,"uid":48060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:34:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf7cf8ed37bf31b227a810947929c851aac16de9","tid":1747692,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a1901274a072ed42490701fab31cddbb87982a","tid":1747692,"uid":239696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:37:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2a0e07c52f8146f6b178dffa543becb6079b99","tid":1747692,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1cb7951fee5c66f3d310fa7e4ad8e5b5b8099cc","tid":1747692,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e23ba29fcb8c4395339e93e9a9098eea53c9d2b","tid":1747692,"uid":81725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:55:47.000Z","msg":"好人一生平安<img