plyTime":"2019-11-23T12:33:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">投票注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有人同我著紅橙黃綠青藍紫白衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有人問你投比咩人/黨派，一定一定要答「建制派」，仲要加多句「反對暴力，希望香港回復和平」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜口號都唔好叫，買包花生番屋企坐定定<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"cf1ddb37324c7e44f114566b496b4d867fea572d","tid":1747692,"uid":206207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:48:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5713a39508f90740dbb2cd5bc05b1e09952c6e3f","tid":1747692,"uid":206207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b71713e1fcf575b9afc7bb2cc786756adf2db6","tid":1747692,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b22f70b009576f3f7f7e7f42336aaf25e4974aa","tid":1747692,"uid":247032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:04:55.000Z","msg":"推 同學仔辛苦晒你 <br />\n見你講野都無氣 好心痛 希望你早d好番"},{"pid":"d14124ddb5bda658a854a4d0e8da0dc4b506d426","tid":1747692,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:04:58.000Z","msg":"屌，上熱門"},{"pid":"3f88683e4a13a6f147ae577d695749ff6812dbea","tid":1747692,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:07:33.000Z","msg":"長期